The paper deals with Distributed Constraint Optimization Problems (DCOPs) and proposes a new algorithm to improve the scalability of an existing algorithm. This falls under the category of Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) and Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing (cs.DC). The proposed algorithm involves coordination among multiple agents, which falls under Multi-Agent Systems (cs.MA). The paper also involves optimization techniques, which falls under Machine Learning (cs.LG) and Systems and Control (cs.SY).
